 EKKEWE CHON ANGANGEN EKKEWE RING .
 _pwe ewe aewin kinikinin .
 Ewe Samonun ekkewe Ring_
 PUK I
 _Sopun 1_
 Eú Pati mi Féfféri
 Nupwen Mr. Bilbo Baggins seni Bag End a esinesin pwe epwene chok
a apwapwaai an engol me eu ierin uputiw ren eu kametip mi sokkolo aucheaan,
a wor chommong poraus me pwapwa lon Hobbiton.
 Bilbo a fokkun pisekisek me fokkun pechekun, me a fen fis ewe amwararen ewe .
Shire ren ukukun wonu ier, seni ewe fansoun a amwarar an mano me ese ekieki .
niwin. Ekkewe pisek a uwei seni an kewe sai ra fen wiliiti eu pisek iei .
legend, me aramas ra luku pwe, ese lifilifil met ekkewe aramas lom lom repwe apasa, pwe .
ewe Chuuk non Bag End a uren ekkewe ttit mi uren pisek auchea. Iwe ika pwe ena .
ese naf an epwe itefoulo, a pwal wor an pochokkul mi langattam pwe epwe mairu ren. Kunok
a wor, nge a usun ita ese kon watte an pochokun ngeni Mr. Lon ipuku ierin a .
chommongun usun chok non fitepuku. Non engon me tiu ier ra poputa ne kori i _well_-
a tumunu, nge _ese siwin_ epwe fen arap ngeni ewe esissin. A wor ekkoch .
pwe ra suki meser me ra ekieki pwe ei a kon watte an ew mettoch mi och; it
a ussun ita pwe ese pwung pwe emon epwe pwal eani (a ussun ita) sarafo esemuch .
usun (reput) pisek ese tongeni much.
 ‘Epwe lamot epwe wor liwinin,’ ra apasa. ‘Esap ina usun, me osukosuk .
epwe feito seni!’
 Nge tori ikenai osukosuk ese mwo feito; me usun Mr. Baggins a kirekiroch ren an .
moni, lape ngeni aramas ra tipemecheres le omusalo an kewe foffor mi sokkolo me an kewe foffor mi murinno .
tufichin. A chok nonnom won an epwe chuuri aramasan kewe (tiwenon chok, enlet,
ekkewe chon Sackville-Baggins), me a wor chommong chon ingeiti i mi tinikken lein ekkewe hobbit .
ekkewe famini mi woungaw me rese auchea. Nge ese wor chienan kewe mi arap ngeni, tori ekkoch leir .
noun kewe cousin mi kukkun ra poputa ne watteta.
 Ewe watte me nein ekkei, me Bilbo a sani, i ewe anuon Frodo Baggins. Inet
Bilbo a tori engon me tiu ierin, a angei Frodo pwe epwe noun chon alemwir, me a uwei ngeni pwe epwe manau .
non ewe Bag; me ekkewe apinukunuk an ekkewe chon Sackville-Baggin ra soposopono ne morono.
Bilbo me Frodo ra fis pwe ra fiti ew chok ranin uputiw, Septemper 22. ‘Ka fen .
mi murino kopwe feito me nonnom ikei, Frodo nei we at,’ a apasa Bilbo non ew ran; ‘iwe mwirin sia tongeni .
fori ach kewe kametipen ranin uputiu fan kinamwe fengen.’ Lon ena atun Frodo a .
a chuen nom non an kewe ierin _tween,_ usun ekkewe hobbit ra eita ngeni ekkewe ierin ruepuku rese wor wiser .
lefilen an kukkun me an epwe watte ierin ipuku-me-ülüngät.
 Pwal engol me ruu ier ra lo. Iteiten ier ekkewe Bagginses ra fen awora liffang mi fokkun manaman .
ekkewe mwichen ranin uputiw mi fitifengen non Bag End; nge iei a weweiti pwe och mettoch .
fokkun amwarar a fen kokkot fan iten ena autumn. Bilbo a fen .
_engol me eu,_ 111, eu nampa mi fokkun amwarar me eu ier mi fokkun itefouno fan iten emon .
hobbit (ewe Took a fen pwisin tori 130); me Frodo a fen .
_ipuku-ülüngät,_ 33) eü nampa mi lamot: ewe rän an ‘feito’.
 Tong ra poputa ne fitikoko non Hobbiton me Bywater; me porausen ewe feito .
mwich a saifetal lon unusen ewe Shire. Ewe uruwo me napanapen Mr.
Baggins a winiti sefan ewe nongonongen porausfengen; me ekkewe aramas mi chinnap .
mwitir chok kuna ar kewe chechemeni non tingor mi etiwa.
 Ese wor emon a kon auseling ngeni lap seni Ham Gamgee mi chinnap, ewe aramas ra silei .
usun ewe Kapas. A fiti ewe _Ewe Ivy Bush_, eu kukkun imwen chon kuno won ewe konik .
aan; iwe a kapas ren ekkoch manaman, pun a fen tumunu ewe atake non Bag .
End ren fitepuku ier, me a fen anisi chinnap Holman non ewe chok angang me mwen ena.
Iei a pwisin chinnapelo me a fitikoko lon ekkewe chuun, ewe angang a .
a akkaewin fis ren noun we at mi kukkun, Sam Gamgee. Iir me rúúemén sam me néún we ra .
fokkun chiechioch ngeni Bilbo me Frodo. Ra nonnom won pwisin ewe Chuuk, lon
Nampa 3 Roun Bag mi chok nom fan ewe Bag End.
 ‘Emon chon fiti ewe mwich mi fokkun murinno me kapas murinno, ina Mr. Bilbo, usun chok ngang mi fen fori fansoun meinisin .
a apasa,’ ewe Gaffer a pwarata. Ren ennet mi unusoch: pun Bilbo a fokkun kirekiroch ngeni .
i, ra eita ngeni ‘Masta Hamfast’, me ra kapas eis ngeni iteitan ussun ewe .
föün iräfölüföl – lon ewe mettoch ‘root’, äkkäeüin potato, ewe
Gaffer a itefouno pwe i ewe sou nemenem mi nap ren meinisin non ewe neni .
(kapachelong pwisin i).
 ‘Nge ifa usun ei Frodo mi nom ren?’ a apasa. a eisini Noakes mi chinnap seni .
By konik. ‘Baggins ina itan, nge a nap seni esopw emon Brandybuck, ra apasa.
A fokkun amwarar ngeniei pwata emon Baggins seni Hobbiton epwe feilo kutta puluwan we towau .
ikewe ie lon Buckland, ikewe aramas ra fokkun sokkolo ie.’
 ‘Me ese mwaal ra queer,’ a apasa Papa Twofoot (ewe chon orun ewe Gaffer), ‘ika ra nonnom won .
ewe epek mi mwaal lon ewe chanpupu Brandywine, me .
pwungun agin ewe Fonufan. Ina eu leeni mi ngau mi rochopwak, ika esopw ekkewe poraus repwe .
pwung.'
 ‘Ka pwung, Papa!’ a apasa. a apasa ewe Kapas. ‘Esap pwe ekkewe Brandybuck seni Buckland ra nonnom _non_ ewe Fonuen Fonufan; nge
ir eu sokkun queer, usun ita. Ra otuputup .
usun ren wa won ena watten konik – me ena esapw fis non napanap. Ekis mairu pwe .
osukosuk a feito seni, ua apasa. Nge ina mwo ika epwe ina, Mr. Frodo a usun chok emon kukkun mi murinno .
hobbit usun chok ka tongeni mochen churi. A fokkun usun chok Mr. Bilbo, me non nap seni .
luku. Mwirin meinisin seman we emon chon Baggins. Emon hobbit mi itefouno mi itefouno ina Mr.
Ekkewe Drogo; ese wor chommong mettoch epwe apasa usun i, tori an a tori ewe konik.’
 ‘Ka fen fiti?’ a apasa fitu mongungu. Ra fen rongorong ei me pwal ekkoch mi rochopwak .
rumor me mwen, ennet; nge ekkewe hobbit ra kan sani uruwoon famili, me .
ra mmonleta ar repwe rongorong sefan. ‘Ewer, ina usun ra apasa,’ ewe Gaffer a apasa. 'En
nengeni: Mr. Drogo, a pupunu ngeni ewe mi woungaw Miss Primula Brandybuck. I ewe Mr.
Bilbo we aewin cousin won pekin ewe in (inan we ewe kukkun seni
ekkewe nengin noun ewe Old Took); me Mr. Drogo a noun we aruwen anuon. Iwe, Mr. Frodo
ina an we aewin _me_ aruwen cousin, fan ew a tou seni ew me ew napanap, usun ewe kapas a apasa,
ika kopwe fitiei. Iwe Mr. Drogo a nom non Brandy Hall ren seman punuwan we, ewe chinnap Masta Gorbadoc,
usun met a kan fori mwirin an pupunu (i
kinikinin an kewe mongo, me Gorbadoc mi chinnap a tumunu eu tengki mi pochokkul mi uren umoumoch); me
a feino _wa_won ewe chanpupu Brandywine; iwe i me punuwan we ra .
a tori, me ewe osupwang Mr. Frodo chok emon semirit me meinisin. '
 ‘Ua fen rongorong pwe ra feino won ewe konik mwirin mongon neanowas non ewe saramen maram,’ a apasa .
Noak mi chinnap; 'me ina ewe weiresin Drogo usun a suki ewe wa.'
 ‘Iwe _Ua_ rongorong pwe a pusin tolong, iwe, a angei mwirin,’ a apasa.
Sandyman, ewe chon angangen Hobbiton.
 ‘Kosapw ausening ngeni meinisin met ka rongorong, Sandyman,’ a apasa ewe Gaffer, ewe .
ese kon lien sani ewe chon ffér. ‘Ese wor eu kokkot pwe epwe feilo kapas ussun pusin .
me pull. Ekkewe wa ra fókkun chéúfetál ngeni chókkewe mi nóm chék nge ese wor .
kutta pwal och popun ewe osukosuk. Iwe nge: a wor ei Mr.
a likitalo emon semirit mi osupwang me a kkuf, ussun chok kopwe tongeni apasa, lein ekkena chon Buckland mi sokkolo,
