Masta Gorbadoc ese mwo wor fansoun a wor kisikis seni fitepuku chiechian lon ewe .
neeni. Mr. Bilbo ese fori ew foffor mi kirekiroch nap seni nupwen a uwei sefani ewe at ngeni
manau lein aramas mi fich.
 ‘Nge ua ekieki pwe a eu minen atakirikir mi ngau ngeni ekkena chon Sackville. Iir
ekieki pwe repwe angei Bag End, ena fansoun nupwen a feino me a
ekieki pwe a fen malo. Iwe mwirin a niwin me a annuku ngenir pwe repwe feino; iwe a sopweno .
