Bilbo a fen kaeo ngeni an kewe taropwe – wewen ese wor feiengau, makkei ngonuk, me ua nuku pwe esap wor .
feiengau epwe feito seni.
 _'Ekkewe Elf me ekkewe Trakon'_ Ua apasa ngeni. '_Kapus me potato ra murino
ren ngang me en. Kosap feilo fiti ewe angangen noum kewe betters, are .
kopwe land non osukosuk mi kon watte ngonuk,’_ua apasa ngeni. Iwe, upwe tongeni apasa ngeni .
ekkoch,’ a apasa sefan ren an nenengeni ewe chon ekis me ewe chon angang.
 Nge ewe Gaffer ese alukuluku ekkewe chon auseling ngeni. Ewe porausen Bilbo
pisek iei a kon pochokkul lon ekiekin ekkewe sarafo lon
hop.
 ‘Ah, nge a fen naf an epwe apacha ngeni met a uwei akkom,’
a anini ewe chon fori, a apasawu ekiekin aramas meinisin. ‘A kan nóm towau seni imwan we. Me
nengeni ekkewe aramas mi sokkolo ra feito ren: ekkewe dwarf ra feito le pwin, me ena .
ewe chon rong mi saifetal, Gandalf, me meinisin. Ka tongeni apasa met ka sani, Gaffer,
nge Bag End ew neni mi amwarar, me aramasan kewe ra amwarar.’
 'Me ka tongeni apasa _met ka_ sani, usun met kese sinei nap seni en .
fori ewe angangen wa, Mr. Sandyman,’ ewe Gaffer a ponueni, ese sani ewe chon fori ewe wa
lap seni ewe fansoun meinisin. Ika pwe ina ewe mettoch queer, iwe sia tongeni fori ren ekis nap seni
queer non ekkei kinikin. Mei wor ekkoch rese towaw seni ar repwe awora ew pint .
of beer ngeni emon chiener, ika ra nonnom lon eu leeni mi wor tittin kolt won. Nge ra fori .
mettoch mi fich ngeni ewe Bag. Ach Sam a apasa pwe _meinisin repwe_ fiti .
ngeni ewe party, iwe epwe wor niffang, mark ngonuk, niffang fan iten meinisin –
ei chok maram usun chok.’
 Ena chok maram a September, me a fokkun murinno usun chok ka tongeni tingor. Eú rán are ruu
mwirin eu poraus (neman a poputa ren ewe Sam mi silelap) a choufetal ussun .
pwe epwe wor fitikoko – fitikoko, met epwe nap seni, usun had .
ese fen kuna lon ewe Shire ren ukukun eu senturi, ese wesewesen fis seni ewe Old .
Took a máló.
 Ran ra no me ewe Ran a arap. Eú wagon mi sókkóló napanapan mi masou ren .
ekkewe packet mi sokkolo lapalaper ra tori Hobbiton lon eu pwinin me ra angang weires won ewe Chuuk .
ngeni Bag End. Ekkewe hobbit mi niuokus ra nenengeni seni ekkewe asam mi lamplit pwe repwe nenengeni. A
a emmweni aramas mi sokkolo, ra kölün köl mi sokkolo: ekkewe dwarf mi wor üfer mi langattam
me ekkewe hood mi alollol. Ekkoch me neir ra nom non Bag End. Lon sopwoloon ewe oruuen .
wiik lon September efoch wa a tolong lon Bywater seni ewe leenien .
Bridge a fis lon rän. Emon mwan chinnap a wawa ewe taraku meinisin. Ii
a úféúf eú úf mi pwechepwech mi chéúfetál, eú úf mi pwechepwech mi langattam, me eú úf mi ffér seni silifer. A wor an .
úfan mi pwechepwech mi langattam me úfan kewe mi chéúfetál mi chéúfetál lúkún chénúpupun an we hat.
Ekkewe kukkun hobbit ra ssa mwirin ewe waimw unusen Hobbiton me tori ewe .
ppan. A wor eu cargo mi uren ekkei, ussun chok ra pwungun ekieki. Non ewe nenien Bilbo
asam ewe mwan chinnap a poputa ne unload: a wor watten chochon ekkewe pisekin maun meinisin .
sokkun me lapalap, iteiten eu me eu a mak won eu G mi watte mi pwechepwech me ewe elf-rune, .
 Ina esissinnen Gandalf, enlet, me ewe chinnap mwan itan Gandalf ewe .
Wizard, ewe a itefoulo lon ewe Shire pokiten an silelap ren ekkei,
smuk, me saram. An we wesewesen business a kon weires me efeiengaw, .
nge ekkewe chon Shire rese sinei och mettoch usun. Me rer i emon chok me lein ekkewe .
‘attrat’ lon ewe Pati. Ina popun ewe pwapwa an ekkewe hobbit-semirit. ‘G
ren Grand!’ ra puchor, me ewe chinnap mwan a menemenoch. Ra silei i ren ar küna, .
ina mwo ika a chok pwa non Hobbiton fan ekkoch me ese mwo tori fansoun nangatam; nge
ir are emon nge ewe mi chinnap seni nour kewe souemwen a fen kuna emon me nein noun kewe .
ekkewe pisekin pwarata – iei ra nom non ewe fansoun nom.
 Nupwen ewe chinnap mwan, a anisi me ren Bilbo me ekkoch chon kukkun, a wes .
unus. Bilbo a ngeni ekkoch moni; nge esap wor eu squib are cracker .
a fis, iwe, a aletipechou ekkewe chon katol.
 ‘Kopwe su seni iei!’ a apasa. a apasa Kantal. ‘Oupwe angei chommong lupwen epwe war ewe fansoun.’
Mwirin a morono non imw ren Bilbo, me ewe asam a suk. Ewe sarafo
hobbits ra nenengeni ewe asam nge ese wor namotan ren ekis fansoun, iwe mwirin ra fori, ra mefi .
pwe ewe ranin ewe kametip esap feito.
 Non Bag End, Bilbo me Gandalf ra mwot non ewe asam mi suk non ew
kukkun ruumw mi nenengeni otiw ngeni ewe atake. Ewe pwinin a saramaram .
me kinamwe. Ekkewe föün irä ra saramaram mi pwechepwech me kolt: snap-dragon me föün irä mi lingöch, .
me ekkewe nasturtium ra chék chéúfetál wóón unusen ewe chénúpupu me ra chék chéúfetál lón ewe chénúpupu .
winto.
 ‘A ifa me saramen om we atake!’ a apasa. a apasa Kantal.
 ‘Ewer,’ Bilbo a apasa. Ua fokkun tongei ennetin, me meinisin ekkewe chinnap mi achengicheng .
Shire; nge ua ekieki pwe mi lamot ngeniei eú holiday.’
 ‘Ka mochen kopwe sopweno ren om kokkot iwe?’ a apasa.
 'Ngang mei. Ua féri ai kefil fitu maram lóóm, me use siwili.’
 ‘A fokkun murinno. Esap chüen wor och kapas mi mürina. Kopwe fiti om kokkot – om .
unusen kokkot, ekiek – me ua nuku pwe epwe fis ngeni ewe mi murino, fan itom, me fan
kich meinisin.’
 'Amwo ita. Iwe nge, ua mochen pwapwaiti pwisin ngang lon ewe Raninfel, me epwe wor ai kukkun
atakirikir.'
 ‘Io epwe takiri, ua ekieki?’ a apasa. a apasa Gandalf, a suki awan.
 ‘Sipwe kuna,’ a apasa Bilbo.
 Lon ewe rän mwirin, pwal ekkoch taraku ra ässäwa ewe Chuuk, me pwal ekkoch taraku. Ikenan
mei wor ekkoch ra ngunungunungau usun ‘foffor non nenier’, nge non ena chok wiik .
ekkewe order ra poputa ne feito seni Bag End ren sokkun pisek meinisin, pisek, ika .
