chon kuno (me ekkewe chon apachanong) non ewe minefoon asam mi pwechepwech non pwisin ir. A ngeni aramas ekkewe liffang .
ngeni meinisin me sundry – ekkewe mwirin ir ekkewe ra feino sefan ren ew aan mi murino me .
a tolong sefan ren ewe asam. Ekkewe Hobbit ra pwisin awora liffang ngeni ekkewe ekkoch aramas .
ranin uputiw. Esap fokkun watte liwinin, usun eu alluk, me esap kon watte liwinin ussun chok won ei .
fansoun; nge esap ina eu kokkot mi ngau. Pwungun pwe lon Hobbiton me Bywater iteiten .
