me ink-in. Milo ese kan pölüweni ekkewe taropwe.
 _Fan iten an ANGELICA epwe aea, seni Uncle Bilbo,_ won ew rong mi uren rong. A
emon Baggins mi kukkun, me a kon ffat pwe a ekieki pwe mesan a lingoch.
