ra fiti ewe Blue. Ikenai, ese mwaal a fen turulong lon eu konik are eu chanpupu .
me feito ngeni eu sopwoloon mi aletipechou, nge esap fokkun fis. Ewe tipis a kon watte .
won Kantal.
