 _Sopun 5_
 Ew Kokkot Ese Mas
 ‘Iei epwe murinno ach sipwe pwisin tori imwach,’ Merry a apasa. A wor och mettoch
pwapwa usun ekkei meinisin, ua kuna; nge epwe witiwit tori ach sipwe tolong.’
 Ra suki ewe aanen Ferry, ewe mi wenechar me pwungun tumun me .
a ffér seni ekkewe faú mi watte mi pwechepwech. Non fitepuku yard ika nap seni a uwei ngenir .
ngeni ewe chuk, ikewe a wor eu leenien ässäw mi för seni irä mi watte. Eú watteen flat .
feri-wa a nom unukun. Ekkewe bollard mi pwechepwech arap ngeni ewe konik .
a saramaram ren saramen ruu lamp won ekkewe puun mi tekia. Mwirin ir ekkewe mist lon .
ekkewe atake mi patapat ra nom iei won ekkewe chuk; nge ewe konik mwen meser a rochopwak, .
ren chok ekkoch chuk mi kkuf usun steam lein ekkewe ira unukkun ewe bank. Ikenan
a ussun ita pwe a kisikisilo foun pwei won ewe epek.
 Merry a emmweni ewe poni won eu al ngeni ewe waimw, me ekkewe ekkoch .
a fiti. Merry a mwitir pusin fiti ew puun mi langattam. Ewe wain Brandy a tori
slow me fitikoko me mwen ir. Lon ewe epek ewe bank a chöüfetäl, nge won a .
ewe aan mi wichiwich a feita seni ewe land mi towau. Lamp ra saramaram ikewe ie.
Mwirin a fis ewe Chuuk Buck; me seni, ra tolong lon ekkewe ppwul mi mwalechelo, .
a saramaram chommong winnach mi pwechepwech, mi pwechepwech me mi pwechepwech. Ir ekkewe winnach lon Brandy .
Hall, ewe imwen ekkewe chon Brandy loom.
 Lom lom Gorhendad Oldbuck, mokuren ewe familien Oldbuck, emon me lein ekkewe mi chinnap
lon ewe Marish are wesewesen lon ewe Shire, ra fen pwerelong lon ewe chanpupu, ina ewe .
popun kiannin ewe fonu ngeni otiu. A aueta (me a forata) ewe imwen Brandy,
a siwili itan ngeni Brandybuck, me a nonnom pwe epwe masta won met a .
arapakan eu kukkun fonu mi pwisin nemeni. An famili a watteta me watteta, me mwirin an
ran a sopweno ne watteno, tori Brandy Hall a angei unusen ewe chuuk mi tekison, .
me a wor ülüngät asam mi watte me mwen, chommong asam mi nom ünükün, me ükükün fitepuku asam.
Iwe, ekkewe Brandybuck me ekkewe chommong chon tumunur ra poputa le ataielo, me mwirin .
pwe repwe aueta, meinisin ra pwellifeili. Ina poputáán Buckland, eú leeni mi chéúfetál .
strip mi nonnom lefilen ewe chanpupu me ewe Fonuen Loom, eu sokkun koloni seni .
ewe Shire. An we sopw mi lapalap, ina Bucklebury, a chufengen lon ekkewe chanpupu me .
slop mwirin ewe imwen Brandy.
 Ekkewe aramas lon ewe fonu Marish ra chiechioch ngeni ekkewe chon Buckland, me ekkewe
nemenemen ewe Mastaan ​​ewe Leenien Mwich (ussun chok mokuren ewe familien Brandybuck .
iteni) a chuen etiwa ekkewe chon atake lefilen Stock me Rushey. Nge
lap ngeni aramasen ewe Shire loom ra ekieki pwe ekkewe chon Buckland ra sokkolo, esopw .
chon ekis usun ita. Inaamwo ika, ren enletin, rese fokkun .
mi sokko seni ekkewe ekkoch hobbit lon ekkewe Fomon. Ekkewe chok non ew chok kinikin:
ra sani ekkewe wa, me ekkoch leir ra tongeni ssa.
