 O! Tom Bomba, Tom Bomba!
 Ren koluk, ren ira me chukuchukuta, ren ira me willow.
 Ren ekkei, akkar me maram, harken iei me rongorong ngenikem!
 Kopwe feito, Tom Bombadil, pun ach osupwang a arap ngenikich!
 Lupwen ra unusen köl ei köl mwirin, a köl ngeniir emön me emön won ewe .
