‘Sam!’ a kokori. ‘Pippin! Pwapwa! Kopwe feito! Pwata kese sópweló le fiti?’
 Ese wor pölüwan. Niuokkus a angei i, iwe, a susefal ngeni ekkewe fau .
a puchor fan song: ‘Sam! Sam! Pwapwa! Pipin!’ Ewe poni a bolt ngeni ewe pwichikar me .
a morolo. Seni eu leeni mi towau, are a ussun ita, a ekieki pwe a rongorong eu puchor: ‘Hoy!
