 Nupwen a achocho ngeni a kokori sefan, me a sopweno ne kokori chommong me chommong .
non netipengaw; nge ese rongorong ponuwan ren ekkoch fansoun, iwe mwirin a usun ita a apwangapwang .
me towau me mwan me tekia won i. ‘Froto! Hoy!’ a feito ekkewe mongungu mi titchik seni .
