pwe epwe tunalo ekkewe kapasen ourour meinisin, me a mochen tipeeu ngeni. Esap ren ewe apilukuluk pwe .
su seni, are an epwe fori och mettoch, mi murinno are ngau: a chok meefi pwe epwe .
angei ewe Ring me isoni won poun. Ese tongeni kapas. A mefi Sam .
nennengeni i, ussun ita nge a silei pwe noun we masta a nom lon och osukosuk watte, nge .
ese tongeni kul ngeni i. A suki mesan me a achocho ngeni ekis fansoun; nge
u ngeni a winiti emon ese tongeni pworacho ngeni, me mwirin a ekis angei ewe sein, me .
a slip ewe Ring won ewe puun mi fiti poun.
