ar kewe mantel ra ufer mi pwechepwech mi langattam; won ufer kewe mi pwechepwech a wor helm seni .
sinfer; lon pour kewe mi apwangapwang a wor ketilas mi for seni steel. Meser kewe ra turutiu won .
me ra suki, nupwen ra suki ngeni. Pokiten a letipechou, a pwisin angei nöün ketilas, .
iwe a usun ngeni i pwe a saramaram, usun ita pwe ew ekkei. Ruu me nein
ekkewe fichi ra fis. Ewe aülümanün a langatam seni ekewe ekoch: möküran a langatam .
me a saramaram me won an we chuk a wor efoch mwaramwar. Lon efoch pöün a amwöchü efoch ketilas mi langattam, .
