 _Sopun 1_
 Chommong Mwich
 Frodo a nennelo me a kuna pwe a rong ewe pet. Akkomwan a ekieki pwe i .
a fen annut lekuniol, mwirin eu tan ese apwapwa mi chuen nom won ewe chuk .
ren memmeef. Are neman a fen semmwen? Nge ewe siling a nikinikin amwarar; mei
flat, me a wor ekkewe föün äsefich mi rochopwak mi lingöch. A chék chéúfetál ekis fansoun .
nennengeni ekkewe kinikinin saramen ewe akkar won ewe tit, me auseling ngeni mongungun emon .
konik.
 `Ia ngang, me ifa ewe fansoun?' a apasa non mongungu ngeni ewe siling. ‘Lon ewe .
Imwen Elrond, me a tori engol awa lekuniol.’ a apasa emon mongungu. `Iei
ewe pwinin October ewe ruwe me fomon, ika ka mochen sinei.’
 `Kandalf!' a puchor Frodo, a mwokut. A wor ewe sou roong mi chinnap, a mwot lon
efoch sea ren ewe asam mi suk.
 `Ewer,' a apasa, `Ngang mi nom ikei. Iwe, ka feioch pwe ka nom ikei, pwal, mwirin meinisin .
ekkewe mettoch mi umwes ka fori seni ewe fansoun ka tou seni imwom.’ Frodo a pwan fiti. Ii
a meefi pwe a kon kinamwe me kinamwe pwe epwe tongeni anini, me ese lifilifil ika ese ekieki .
epwe angei ewe feioch seni eu anini. A unusen nennelo iei, me ewe chechemeni .
ren an sai a niwin: ewe `chon mwochomwoch’ mi efeiengaw ren ewe Old .
For ewe `aksiten' non _Ewe Poni mi Pran_; me an mwaken ren an ufouf .
ewe Ring non ewe dell fan ewe Puun. Nupwen a ekieki usun ekkei meinisin .
mettoch me achocho nge ese wor lamotan pwe epwe uwei an chechemeni ngeni an tori ewe 1990.
Rivendell, a wor eu fansoun langattam, a atai chok ren ekkewe puun mi mosonoson seni .
Paip an Gandalf, nupwen a suki ekkewe fitikoko mi pwechepwech seni ewe asam.
 ‘Ia Sam a nom ie?’ a apasa. Frodo a eisini non fansoun nangatam. ‘Nge ekkewe ekkoch ra pwung?’ a apasa.
 ‘Ewer, ir meinisin ra safe me pochokun,’ Gandalf a ponuweni. `Sam a nom ikei tori 1990.
Ua tinalo pwe epwe ekis asoso, orun esopw awa a lo.’
 `Met a fis non ewe Ford?' a apasa Frodo. `Meinisin a usun ita mi fokkun dim non ekkoch napanap;
me a chúen ina usun.’
 ‘Ewer, epwe ina usun. Iwe a poputa ne morono,’ Gandalf a ponuweni. ‘Ewe mwáál .
a akkufukemi mwirin. Ekkoch awa me kopwe fen tori .
ach aninis. Nge mi wor ekkoch pochokun non en, nei hobbit mi achengicheng! Usun met ka pwarata non
ewe Bar. Ina ewe touch me feino: eni ewe fansoun mi kon efeiengaw nap seni meinisin. Ngang
ika kopwe tongeni fiti ewe mwich lon Weathertop.’
