ikenan. Mwirin a wor kinamwe, me ese wor kapas a feito seni Moria seni ena fansoun.
 "Iwe, arapakan ew ier a no emon chon kuno a feito ngeni Dáin, nge esap seni Moria –
seni Mordor: emon chon wawa oris non ewe pwinin, ewe a kori Dáin ngeni an we asam. Ewe Samon
Sauron ewe mi Lapalap, ina minne a apasa, a mochen pwe sipwe chiechioch. Ring epwe ngeni .
ren ena, usun chok a ngeni me nom. Iwe, a eisini fän mwittir usun _hobbits_, usun .
met sokkun ir, me ia ra nom ia. “Pun Sauron a sinei,” a apasa, “pwe .
emon me nein ekkei a fen sinei ngonuk non ew fansoun."
 ‘Ren ei mettoch aia fokun niuokus, pwe aisap pölüeni. Iwe mwirin an .
fell mongungun a kukkununo, me epwe fen sweet ika pwe a tongeni. "Usun emon
kukkun esisinen chok om chiechi Sauron a eisini ei," a apasa: "pwe en .
epwe kuna ei chon sola," ina usun an kapas, "me angei seni i, mochen ika ese mochen, .
efoch kukkun ring, ewe mi kisikis seni ekkewe ring, pwe fan eu a solani. A chok eu mettoch mi kukkun pwe .
Sauron a fangeta, me eu pwonen om mochen mi murinno. Kopwe kuna, me ülüngät ring .
pwe ekkewe Dwarf sires mi nom rer me lom repwe liwinitikemi, me ewe muu .
seni Moria epwe noumi feinfeino chok. Kopwe chok kutta porausen ewe chon sola, ika a .
a chuen manau me ia, iwe, epwe wor liwinin watte me chiechioch mi nomofoch .
seni ewe Samon. Kopwe ú ngeni, iwe mettóch resap fókkun múrinné. Ka ú ngeni?"
