 ‘Iwe, Glorfindel a apasa, ‘sipwe aturalong lon ewe leeni mi alollol, iwe, sipwe fori ewe .
kapas chofona seni Saruman a fis. Pun a ffat iei pwe pwal mwo nge lon ewe Mwichen Sou Pwungupwung an .
pechen kewe ra fen nom won eu al mi kkuf. A sinei pwe ewe Ring ese pout seni .
fansoun meinisin, nge a mochen pwe sipwe ekieki ena; pun a poputa ne mocheniaiti fan itan pwisin i. Chiwen
fan chommong lon kapas chofona ewe enlet a monomon: lon ewe Sea epwe lukulukoch.’
 `Ese wor feinfeino chok,’ a apasa Gandalf. `A wor chommong mettoch lon ewe leeni mi alollol .
konik; me ekkewe matau me fonu repwe tongeni siwin. Iwe esap wisach ikei ach sipwe angei .
ekieki chok ren eu fansoun, are ren ekkoch manauen Aramas, are ren eu ier mi lo .
ewe fonufan. Sipwe kutta eu sopwoloon ei minen efeiengau, inaamwo ika sise apilukuluk .
pwe epwe fori eu.’
 ‘Me ena sisap kuna won ekkewe aan ngeni ewe Sea,’ a apasa Galdor. 'Ika
ewe liwin ngeni Iarwain epwe ekieki pwe a kon efeiengaw, iwe, ewe sái ngeni ewe Séa a fis iei .
a ur ren feiengau mi fokkun watte. Netipei a ereniei pwe Sauron epwe ekieki pwe sipwe .
angei ewe aanen otiw, nupwen a sinei met a fis. Epwe mwittir fis. Ekkewe Niwinin
ra fen wesewesen fiti oris nge ina chok eu asoso, mwen repwe kuna minefoon oris .
me mwitir. Ewe chok manamanen Gondor mi kisikisilo a uta iei lefilen i me emon .
march non pochokun won ekkewe sat ngeni ewe Notou; Iwe, are epwe feito, epwe maun ngeni ewe .
Ekkewe Tower mi pwechepwech me ekkewe Haven, mwirin ei ekkewe Elves eli esap wor ar leenien su seni ewe .
langattam ekkewe saram lon ewe Fonufan Lefilen.’
