fitikoko lon ewe asepwal.
 `Ekkewe man ra pwan!' a apasa Aragorn, a pwarata ngeni fan.
 ‘Ese tongeni anisi ena iei,’ a apasa Gandalf. `Ika pwe ir mi murinno ika .
ngaw, ika ese wor met epwe fis ngeni kich, sipwe chok feitiw non ew chok fansoun. Esap mwo
won ekkewe föün Caradhras sipwe witiwiti pwal eü pwinin-pwin!’
 Eú ásepwál mi pwichikar a chéúfetál mwirin, atun ra chék chéúfetál wóón ewe
Ewe Asamalapen Redhorn, me a turutiw ren apwangapwang won ewe chuk. Karadras a fen akkufu .
iir.
 _Sopun 4_
 Ew Sai non ewe Rochopwak
 A tori pwinin, me ewe saram mi pwechepwech a pwal mwittir kisikisilo, lupwen ra .
a chék chéúfetál fán iten ewe pwinin. Ra fókkun letipechou. Ekkewe chuuk ra veil lon .
a pwichikar, me ewe asepwal a pwichikar. Gandalf a amanaua ir pwal eu mongungu
emon me emon ekkewe miruvor an Rivendell. Nupwen ra mongo ekkoch mongo a kori emon .
konsen.
 ‘Sise tongeni, ennetin, sopweno sefan non ei pwinin,’ a apasa. `Ewe atake won ewe .
Ewe Asamalapen Redhorn a fen asongakich, iwe, sipwe asoso ikei ren ekis fansoun.’
 `Iwe mwirin ia sipwe feilo ie? ’ a eisini Frodo.
 ‘A chuen wor ach sai me ach angang mwen mesach,’ Gandalf a ponuweni.
