mwirin ir. Ra nom lon eu al mi alolol lefilen ekewe lesopun ewe tit, nge .
ra mwitir fetan non ra tonong non ewe Telinimwen ekkewe Ira. Ese wor aramas ra tongeni
ra kuna, are rongorong och pechen won ekkewe aan; nge a wor chommong mongungu, usun .
ir, me non ewe asepwan asan. Towau won ewe chuuk ra tongeni rongorong ewe mongungu .
