 _Sopun 8_
 Pwan feino ngeni Lórien
 Non ena pwinin ewe Kompani a koko sefan ngeni ewe rumwen Celeborn, me .
ikewe ie ewe Samon me ewe Fefin ra kapong ngenir ren kapas mi murino. Ren enletin, Celeborn a kapas .
ren ar feilo.
 `Iei ewe fansoun,' a apasa, `lupwen ekkewe ra mochen sopweno ewe Quest .
repwe apochokuna netiper pwe repwe tou seni ei fonu. Chokkewe rese chüen mochen feilo .
forward epwe tongeni nom ikei, ren ekis fansoun. Nge ika repwe nonnom are feilo, esap wor emon epwe tongeni .
sure ren kinamwe. Pun iei sia tori lesopolan feiengau. Iei ekkewe mi mochen .
epwe tongeni witiwiti warotoon ewe awa tori an epwe suuk ekkewe alen fonufan .
sefan. are sia koriir ngeni ewe amuchunon osupwangen Lórien. Iwe, eli repwe liwiniti .
pwisin fonuer kewe, are repwe feilo ngeni ewe leeni mi langattam fan iten ekkewe mi malo lon maun.’
 A wor eu kinamwe. `Ir meinisin ra finata pwe repwe feino mwach,’ a apasa Galadriel .
nenengeni non meser kewe.
