 _Sopun 10_
 Ewe Kinikinin ewe Mwichen Aramas .
 Aragorn a emwenir ngeni ewe puun. Iei won an we west .
pekin fan ewe saram an Tol Brandir eu ira mi pwechepwech a tori ewe konik seni .
ekkewe pechen Amon Hen. Mwirin, a fis ekkewe aewin chuuk mi mosonoson .
ren ira, me ira ra fetan ngeni otiw won ekkewe chuk mi uren .
chenupwupu. Ew kukkun spring a turutiw me a amongouni ewe fetil.
 ‘Iei sipwe asoso non ei pwinin,’ Aragorn a apasa. `Iei ewe fönüen Part .
Galen: eu leeni mi pwung lon ekkewe ranin summer lom lom. Sipwe apilukuluk pwe esap wor och mettoch mi ngau a fen .
nge kopwe feito ikei.’
 Ra äeä nöür kewe wa won ekewe föün irä mi pwechepwech, nge ünükür ra föri .
ar we mwich. Ra anomu chon mas, nge resap küna ika rongorong chon oputer. Ika
Gollum a fen ekiekin tapweno mwirir, a chok nomw nge ese kuna me rongorong.
Iwe nge, atun ewe pwinin a tori Aragorn, a chék chéúfetál, iwe a chéúfetál fán chómmóng lón an we .
annut me rong. Non ekkewe kukkun awa a uta me feito ren Frodo, ewe an fansoun .
ina pwe epwe mammasa.
 `Pwata ka chék chéúfetál? ’ a eisini Frodo. `Esap ina om we watte.'
 `Use sinei,’ Aragorn a ponuweni; `nge eu saram me eu minen efeiengau a fen
a watteta non ai we rong. Epwe murinno ika kopwe angei noum ketilas.’
 `Pwata? ’ a apasa Frodo. `Ekkewe chon oput ra nom reom? '
 `Sipwe nengeni met Sting epwe tongeni pwarata,’ Aragorn a ponuweni.
 Frodo a mwitir angei ewe elf-blade seni an we chuk. Ren an letipechou ekkewe epek .
a saramaram lon ewe pwinin. `Ekkewe Ork! ’ a apasa. `Ese fokkun arap, nge inaamwo
arap ngeni, a ussun ita.’
 `Ua niuokus usun chok,’ Aragorn a apasa. `Nge eni rese nom won ei pekin .
ewe Chanpupu. Ewe saramen Sting a chék chéúfetál, me eli epwe chék chéúfetál ngeni ekkewe spai .
seni Mordor mi fetan won ekkewe chukun Amon Lhaw. Ngang use mwo rongorong me mwan usun .
Ork won Amon Hen. Nge io a sinei met epwe tongeni fis non ekkei ran mi ngaw, iei pwe .
Minas Tirit ese chúen apéchékkúla ekkewe leenien Anduin. Sipwe fokkun feilo
nesor.'
 Ewe rän a feito usun ekkei me ötüöt. Lon ewe East a wor ekkewe bar mi pwechepwech .
seni kuchu usun chök äsepwälin eu ekkei mi watte. Ewe akkar mi ttin a saramaram seni .
fan ren ekkei mi pwechepwech; nge ekiselo chok a feita won ir ngeni eu leeni mi ffat .
fan nang. Ewe chukun Tol Brandir a tipeni kolt. Frodo a nenengeni ewe epek
me a nenengeni ewe fonu mi tekia. Pekin kewe ra chéúfetál seni ewe konik mi chéúfetál.
Tekia won ekkewe chuuk mi tekia a wor ekkewe chuuk mi tekia ekkewe ira ra feita won,
fiti ew mokuran won pwan ew; iwe, won ir a pwal wor mesen aramas mi pwechepwech seni .
fau ese tongeni tori, a wor eu watten ttit mi for seni fau. Chommong man ra pwellifeili .
usun, nge ese wor esissinnen ekkewe ekkoch mettoch mi manau ra tongeni kuna.
 Nupwen ra wes ne mongo, Aragorn a kori ewe Kompan pwe repwe chufengen. `Ewe ran a
feito mwirin,’ a apasa: ‘ewe ranin kefil minne sia fen amwokutu fansoun langattam. Met
epwe iei winiti ach ewe Kompany mi sai tori towaw non chiechi? Sipwe
sia su ngeni otiw fiti Boromir me feino ngeni ekkewe maunen Gondor; ika kopwe suki ngeni otiw ngeni ewe .
Niuokus me Saram; are sipwe atai ach chiechifengen me feino ei me ena usun .
emon me emon epwe tongeni filata? Met chok sia fori epwe chok mwitir fis. Sisap tongeni nóm ikei ie.
Ewe chon koum a nom won ewe sat otiw, sia sinei; nge ua niuokkus pwe ekkewe Orc repwe tongeni .
a fen nom won ei pekin ewe konik.’
 A wor eu fansoun langattam mi kinamwe nge esap wor emon a kapas are mwokut.
 ‘Ewer, Frodo,’ Aragorn a apasa mwirin. `Ua nuokus pwe ewe chou a nom won
en. En ewe Chon Angang mi kefinita me ren ewe Mwichen Sou-Pwungupwung. Om pwisin napanap en chok ka tongeni .
fini. Lon ei mettoch üsap tongeni öüröürakemi. Ngang sap Gandalf, me ina mwo ika ngang
ra fen achocho le uwei wisan, use silei met sokkun kokkot are apilukuluk a wor ren ei .
awa, ika pwe mi enlet pwe a wor. Lap ngeni a ussun ita pwe ika a nom ikei iei ewe .
kefil epwe chuen witiwit ngonuk. Ina usun om fate.’
 Frodo ese ponuweni non ew chok fansoun. Iwe, a kapas fän mosonoson. `Ua sinei pwe mwitir ina
mi lamot, nge use tongeni filatá. Ewe chou a chou. Kopwe ngeniei eu awa, me .
Ngang upwe kapas. Kopwe mut ngeniei ai upwe chék nóm! '
 Aragorn a nenengeni ren kirekiroch. `A fokkun murinno, Frodo noun Drogo,'
a apasa. `Epwe wor ew awa, iwe kopwe chok nom. Sipwe nom ikei .
ren och fansoun. Nge kosap rikilo towau are towau.’
 Frodo a mwot ekis me a suki awan. Sam, ewe a fen nennengeni .
noun we masta ren an watte an osukosuk, a suki awan me a ngungures: ‘A ffat usun emon .
Pike, nge ese och Sam Gamgee epwe fori an kapas iei chok.’ ,
 Iei chok Frodo a uta me a fetan; iwe Sam a kuna pwe nupwen ekkewe ekkoch .
ra nemeni pwisin ir me rese nennengeni i, mesen Boromir a tapwelo mwirin .
Frodo a achocho, tori an a pass seni an epwe kuna non ekkewe ira non pechen Amon .
Hen.
 A fetan fetan ese wor an mochen akkomw non ewe ira, Frodo a kuna pwe pechen kewe ra .
a emmweni i ngeni ekkewe chuk. A feito ngeni eu al, ewe .
