 A mwot won ewe fau me a apachanong poun kewe, a nenengeni .
ngeni otiw nge a kuna ekis chok ren mesan. Meinisin met a fis seni Bilbo .
likiti ewe Shire a fetan non an ekiek, me a chechemeni me ekieki .
