ese kon arap ngeni eu kefil.
 Fan eu a nennelo seni an ekiek: eu memef mi amwarar a feito ngeni pwe .
och mettoch a nom mwirin, pwe mesen aramas rese chiechioch ra nom won. A chék chéúfetál me .
a tur; nge meinisin met a kuna ren an mairu ina Boromir, me mesan a .
smile me kirekiroch.
 `Ua nuokus fan itom, Frodo,’ a apasa, a feito me mwen. `Ika Aragor a
pwung me Orcs ra arap, iwe esap wor emon me neich epwe chok fetan, me en mi kisikis seni .
meinisin: ina popun a anongonong won en. Iwe, letipei a pwal chou. Amwo upwe nom iei me .
kapas ekis, seni ai kunakemi? Epwe aururu letipei. Ia mei wor .
ina popun chommong, kapas meinisin ra wiliiti eu anini ese much. Nge ruuemon repwe tongeni .
kutta tipatchem.’
 `Ka kirekiroch,’ Frodo a ponuweni. ‘Nge use ekieki pwe och kapas epwe .
anisi ei. Pun ua sinei met upwe fori, nge ua nuokus ai upwe fori, Boromir:
nuwokus.'
 Boromir a uta fan kinamwe. Rauros a rokopwanieno. Ewe asepwal a ngungures lon .
ekkewe panen ekkewe ira. Frodo a ngungures.
 Iwe, Boromir a feito o mottiu ünükün. `Ka nukuw pwe kese
riaffou nge ese wor lamotan? ’ a apasa. `Ua mochen anisuk. A lamot ngonuk kapasen fén lón óm .
kefil mi weires. Kosap angei mine? '
 ‘Ua ekieki pwe ua fen silei met sokkun fon kopwe awora, Boromir,’ a apasa .
Frodo. ‘Me epwe ussun ita tipatchem nge fan iten ewe ourour lon letipei.’
 `Ourour? Ourour ngeni met? ’ a apasa Boromir fän pöchökkül.
 ‘Ungeni ewe fansoun. Ungeni ewe aan mi usun ita mecheres. Ach sipwe ú ngeni ewe .
chou mi nom won ngang. Ungeni-ewer, ika epwe apasa, ungeni nukunuk non .
ewe pochokun me ennet an Aramas.’
