won ekkewe chuuk mi pwechepwech non ewe Emyn Muil, me tonong non ewe Fonuen Saram.
 _Iei a much ewe aewin kinikinin uruon ewe Maunen Ring._
 _Ewe oruuen kinikin a iteni_EKKEWE RUU TOWE_, pokiten ekkewe mettoch mi fis lon ewe ier 1990.
ra nemeni_ORTHANC_, ewe imwen maun itan Saruman, me ewe imwen maun
of_MINAS MORGUL_ ewe a tumunu ewe asam mi monomon ngeni Mordor; a aporausa usun ewe .
foffor me feiengauen meinisin chon ewe mwicheich mi mufesen iei, tori ewe .
feito seni ewe Rochopwak mi Lapalap._
 _Ewe aulungatin kinikin a aporausa usun ewe amuchunon tumun ngeni ewe Shadow, me ewe soponon .
ewe misin an ewe chon uwei Ring non_EWE CHON ANGANGEN EWE KING.
